<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, December 8 (Xinhua) -- The general price index on
Tehran Stock Exchange Tuesday closed at 1558.86, up 0.05 points
from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 886,896 shares changed hands and the turnover
reached 2.68 billion rials (about 446,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
And shares of 13 companies gained while those of 16 others
declined. 
</P>
