<HEADLINE> Sensitive Index on BSE Gains 4.57 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 9 (Xinhua) -- The sensitive index on the
Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE) market Wednesday closed at 2,950.21
points as against Tuesday's close of 2,945.64, netting a small
gain of 4.57 points.
