and 118.44 respectively.
</P>
<P>
Equities generally lost their initial gains but smart gains in
index heavyweights like hind lever, reliance industries and
others, attributed to fresh support from institutional investors,
held the sensitive index just above last close on the stock market
Wednesday. 
