Zabaleta and his girlfriend had travelled from San Sebastian
to the game in Madrid and had gone to a bar before the match.
</P>
<P>
When a group of skinheads saw the woman's Real Sociedad scarf,
they started shouting insults at the couple and followed them out
of the bar.
</P>
<P>
The men attacked Zabaleta who was stabbed through the heart to
die several hours later in a Madrid hospital, reports said.
