United Nations of trying to cover up the genocide against Tutsis
in Rwanda in 1994. He has presented a confidential memorandum of
the U.N. force in Kigali and a letter by a French general leading
the Casques Bleus peace keeping force in Rwanda, both of which
showed that the U.N. was fully aware of the genocide at that
time. 
