<HEADLINE> South Korea Wins Men's 90-kg Judo Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 9 (Xinhua) -- Yoo Sung-Yeon South Korea took
the men's 90-kg judo title at the 13th Asian Games here Wednesday
evening.
</P>
<P>
Japan's Yoshio Nakamura finished second for a silver medal.
</P>
<P>
The bronze medal was shared by D. Purevsuren of Mongolia and
Kamol Murodov of Uzbekistan. 
</P>
</TEXT>
