<HEADLINE> Chen Yanqing Breaks Clean and Jerk World Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 9 (Xinhua) -- Chen Yanqing of China took the
women's 58kg class weightlifting title at the 13th Asian Games
here on Wednesday.
</P>
