<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 9 (Xinhua) -- Chen Yanqing of China won the
58kg class women's weightlifting title with a total of 220
kilograms at the 13th Asian Games here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Ri Song Hui of DPR Korea, who broke the clean and jerk world
record with a lift of 125 kilograms, finished second at 217.5
kilograms, followed by Suta Khassaraporn of Thailand at 210.
</P>
