<DOCNO> XIE19981209.0248 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-09 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Urgent  Mongolian Parliament Approves Nonimation of PM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ULAN BATOR, December 9 (Xinhua) -- The Great Hural (parliament)
of Mongolia Wednesday approved the nomination of Janlaviin
Narantsatsralt as the country's prime minister.
</P>
<P>
The Great Hural approved the nomination submitted by President
Nachagyn Bagabandy with 36 votes for and 21 against. 
</P>
