<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Asian Games Bowling Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 9 (Xinhua) -- Following are the Asian Games
tenpin bowling results here on Wednesday:
</P>
<P>
Men's singles:
</P>
<P>
1. Prasert Panturat, Thailand, 1,362 points
